                            <span class="session-time">5:00 PM - 6:00 PM EST</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="session-description">Dr. Sarah Johnson and recovered patient Robert Davis discuss practical lifestyle adjustments for diabetes management.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Session 3 -->
                    <div class="session-card">
                        <h3 class="session-title">Heart Attack Survivors Support Group</h3>
                        <div class="session-info">
                            <span class="session-date">March 15, 2025</span>
                            <span class="session-time">1:00 PM - 2:30 PM EST</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="session-description">A panel of heart attack survivors share their stories and answer questions about recovery and lifestyle changes.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Session 4 -->
                    <div class="session-card">
                        <h3 class="session-title">Mental Health Recovery: Breaking the Stigma</h3>
                        <div class="session-info">
                            <span class="session-date">March 22, 2025</span>
                            <span class="session-time">4:00 PM - 5:30 PM EST</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="session-description">Lisa Wong discusses her journey through depression and anxiety, and how she found healing through therapy and community support.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Session 5 -->
                    <div class="session-card">
                        <h3 class="session-title">Living with Chronic Pain: Strategies and Hope</h3>
                        <div class="session-info">
                            <span class="session-date">March 28, 2025</span>
                            <span class="session-time">3:00 PM - 4:00 PM EST</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="session-description">Michael Torres shares practical strategies for managing chronic pain and maintaining quality of life after a serious back injury.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="attend-section">
                    <h3 class="attend-title">Join Our Live Sessions</h3>
                    <p>Connect with recovered patients and healthcare professionals to gain insights, ask questions, and find support.</p>
                    
                    <div class="zoom-info">
                        <p><strong>Zoom Meeting ID:</strong> 123 456 7890</p>
                        <p><strong>Password:</strong> Healing2025</p>
                        <p><strong>Link:</strong> https://zoom.us/j/1234567890</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <button class="attend-button">Attend a Live Session</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
<section class="guidelines">
    <div class="container"></div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Government Guidelines for Patient Benefits</h2>
    <div class="options">
        <div class="option">
            <button class="option-button">Medical Insurance Benifit</button>
